# 2.1.0 - 2007/10/01

- fixed some bugs in the GUI
- now the histogram is drawn wirh a red gradient in order to highlight the values ranges
- now it's possible to choose the image format to use when a new image is loaded
- added support for 8-bit color images
- added support for big images, when an image is bigger than the screen it's scaled properly
- added Edit->Settings menu
- more checks on images loading for single images and sequences


# 2.0.1 - 2007/05/09

- fixed a bug related to images loading
- fixed a division by 0 bug in histogram computation
- now histogram is updated when a ROI exists and user changes the current slice
